snippet.title: GlobalWahrman
snippet.description:
GlobalWahrman on Youtube is a collection of videos that illustrate themes and commentary found on the blog GlobalWahrman.blogspot.com.

In general we discuss the history of computer animation, visual effects, the cold war, intelligence, film criticism and theory, sword fighting in cinema and many other topics.

Welcome.
